title: Received Season Rewards, but no Victorious Maokai?
body:
Hello everyone,

I recently received my ranked season rewards. I got Gold V this year and expected to get Victorious Maokai, and checked to see it still saying 'Unavailable'. I did however get a golden border, icon, and the champion himself, as I didn't own him. Is this a mistake? Or have I simply not gotten it yet?

Thanks!

replies.body: I looked into this for you, and everything looks okay to me!  Let me know if this is still an issue.  :D
i haven't gotten anything even though I got to gold before preseason started, is there an bug or something or did I just hit gold too late? Thanks!{{champion:57}} {{item:3070}}

I did have a previous response for you but I was looking at the current preseason; oops.  I do see you placed in time, so hit us up in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) and we can help!  We're happy to add rewards to eligible players in case it was missed!

> I looked into this for you, and everything looks okay to me!  Let me know if this is still an issue.  :D

Same happened to me and i still do not have Victorious Maokai but i got every other reward such as Maokai.
I'm getting worried :( I got into gold 5 (0 lp) before preseason, I haven't received any rewards; the icon, the plates not to mention the skin.
Having this issue as well. I'll stay patient and wait I suppose.
I havent received anything yet :/ No boarder no icon :(
Likewise.  Very first ranked season and I managed to hit Platinum.  Received everything, including Maokai,, besides the Victorious skin.
exactly same as me! {{item:3070}}
No Skin FeelsBadMan {{champion:57}} {{item:3070}}

...SAME HERE...I GOT EVERYTHING EXCEPT  SKIN....
I have the same issue, i recieved the icon, the champion but not the skin its weird to me this didnt happened last year :/
Same :(

I know a few are still missing their skin, but rest assured everything is still on the way.  Rewards are still being distributed to many players, and we're not done.  You may see some getting all of their rewards before others, but hang tight.  Gold+ eligible players will get their victorious skin!
same here

You look all set too!  If anyone is still missing an item, give it some time for everything to finish rolling out.  Our aim is still to have this wrapped up by the 21, per the [Season 6 FAQ](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/page/2016-ranked-season-ends-soon).
